Class Admin

java.lang.Object
assegnamento3.src.Person
assegnamento3.src.LoggableUser
assegnamento3.src.Admin
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Admin
extends LoggableUser
The class Admin represents an instance of an Admin of the WineShop.

He can see all information about customers, sellers, wines, and orders.

Admins can add sellers and edit their information.

It extends LoggableUser to implement the functionalitity to be logged in.
